## ğŸŒ¿ Environment variables

| Variable            | Effect                                      |
|---------------------|---------------------------------------------|
| `TELERT_LONG`       | Default threshold (seconds) for `hook`.     |
| `TELERT_SILENT=1`   | Suppress stdout/stderr echo in `run`.       |

